          OUTPUT FORMAT (JSON ONLY):
          {
            "message": "Question text (natural and including definition)...",
            "options": ["Yes ✅", "No ❌"] (OR empty array [] if asking for amount)
          }

          Final JSON Format (When list is exhausted):
          {
            "message": "Final analysis text...",
            "isFinal": true,
